Accessing database
=========================

1. Open command line
2. mysql -u super -p [Super is a user who manages the database]
3. [Press enter]
4. use hostscanner;
Some Useful commands in sql
-----------------------------
show tables [Displaying all tables of the database]
desc users  [Showing details of the tables like columns and datatypes]
select * from users [show all data in table users (this table can be changed to others like ip_groups,hosts....)]


Running project
---------------------
1. Open command line
2. cd Desktop/hostscanner
3. source venv/bin/activate [Activating virtual environment which store libraries]
4. python app.py

Running scanner.py to keep scanning hosts connected and disconnected
-----------------------------------------------------------------------
1. Open command line
2. cd Desktop/hostscanner
3. source venv/bin/activate [Activating virtual environment which store libraries]
4. python controllers/Scanner.py

